metadata.name: Paradise
metadata.description:
Paradise - By AwfulEye : Sitting off the coast of a warm white sandy beach with crystal clear water. There is a tranquil Island. It looks small but what lies underneath is pure Paradise, Swimming with WHALES! 

This 1 of 1 was created by a legally blind artist, I have a rare eye condition called axenfeld-rieger syndrome, which caused Glaucoma!

Find out more at awfuleye.com
